title: Barry Zito does well in his final start; A’s beat Angels 8-7
text:
Photo: Stephen Dunn, Getty Images Barry Zito of the Oakland Athletics throws a pitch against the Los Angeles Angels of Anaheim at Angel Stadium of Anaheim on September 30, 2015 in Anaheim, California.
Barry Zito of the Oakland Athletics throws a pitch against the Los...
ANAHEIM — Barry Zito didn’t qualify for the win in what was probably his final big-league start. He gets the proverbial game ball, though, for his work against the red-hot Angels.
